{"tid":2349902,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美候任財長耶倫 兩年演講收入逾5400萬港元","createTime":"2021-01-02T02:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T04:59:04.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2204968088520022a00238fdc7eb0cb7dd3483a0","tid":2349902,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T02:11:11.000Z","msg":"美國前聯儲局主席耶倫，獲總統當選人拜登挑選為新內閣財長，她過去兩年透過演講，賺取700萬美元(5460萬港元)。邀請她演講的機構包括花旗、高盛、谷歌等大型企業。<br />\n<br />\n耶倫在2014至2018年期間擔任聯儲局主席，她在2019及2020年主要收入來自演講費。美國政府操守委員會日前公布，耶倫通過拜登政權過渡團隊，向委員會提交3份財務資料。<br />\n<br />\n耶倫在另一份財務文件中，披露她持有的上市證券組合，以及曾向她支付演講費的銀行名單。耶倫向委員會承諾，在處理相關企業事務時，將尋求委員會書面批准。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2675358\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2675358&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=92e75231\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2675358</a>"},{"pid":"4f23f1f66cdd3c3f6d42f848842ba849ab473833","tid":2349902,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T02:44:15.000Z","msg":"前幾任個幾個IBANK出身演講收幾$?"},{"pid":"612c58c48c9943aa527575f817f375f8cf762581","tid":2349902,"uid":347237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T03:41:35.000Z","msg":"conflict of interests is no longer an issue in coming Biden presidency"},{"pid":"401924f8b90d403723969543d7c96b4b7dd1ab94","tid":2349902,"uid":140893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"612c58c48c9943aa527575f817f375f8cf762581","tid":2349902,"uid":347237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T03:41:35.000Z","msg":"conflict of interests is no longer an issue in coming Biden presidency"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T04:33:00.000Z","msg":"其實一向都係咁，大把總統就係靠演講攞延後利益"},{"pid":"5165ccdbe60b97abc307b7644e631bda2fd061b4","tid":2349902,"uid":347237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"401924f8b90d403723969543d7c96b4b7dd1ab94